metadata.name: Kirby #1/25
metadata.description:
Hand drawn, mixed media illustration.  
The piece title 'Kirby' is the genesis piece in the collection titled RSC Collection (Rescue). The piece was created utilising many textures. I wanted the piece to be raw and unedited.  
The sale of this piece and all pieces in the RSC Collection will help people who are doing amazing work in helping our animal friends in need. "Kirby" has been created for Kirby's Calf Rescue with 50% of the sale of this piece going to help them with bills.
